standard (built-in) Java annotation @Override example

Here’s a clean list of the most common built-in Java annotations:

## Compile-time (SOURCE)

* `@Override`
* `@SuppressWarnings`

## Runtime (RUNTIME)

* `@Deprecated`
* `@FunctionalInterface`
* `@SafeVarargs`
* `@Retention`
* `@Target`
* `@Documented`
* `@Inherited`

## Class-level (CLASS)

* `@Generated`


